title: nightingale and the rose
description:
Since i collect female vocals of many kinds, i figured some of you would enjoy this. I heard it on a radio show on my classical radio station and it took me quite a while to find out where and how to buy it....i finally found it on amazon dot com as a download, so i bought it. This song can be used as a deadly weapon or to keep pests away.

Enjoy

Song Has The Following Practical Uses

*Repel Pests
*Drive Away Unwanted Guests (Your Wife or Girlfriend's Annoying Fat Girlfriends)
*Annoy The Living Shit Out Of People Who Piss You Off
*Cause Drunken Friends Or Relatives To Go And Sleep It Off Elsewhere
*An Offensive Weapon That Is Completely Legal And Yet Wont DMame, Kill Or Draw Blood...Yet They May Beg You to Turn It Off or beg you to Shoot Them.
